<span id="freeTextContainer8336569174849742838"><strong>Always a great story ensues </strong><br/><br/>Cadfael leaves his Herb garden to act as interpreter in Wales and ends up looking into a murder, escorting a bride-to-be and becoming a captive to Danes cheated of payment in a squabble between brothers over land. And he thought he would have a quiet life in the cloister! </span>

